---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

---
<Base
  title="CGM Distribution Partnership &mdash;EverCheck"
  description="Partner with EverCheck to distribute advanced CGM solutions worldwide. Expand your healthcare portfolio, accelerate market entry, and build stronger margins."
>


<!-- ===== NAVIGATION ===== -->


<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img src="/distribution-hero.jpg" alt="Abstract global distribution network with interconnected nodes, world maps, and logistics icons including cargo ship and airplane on dark blue background">
  </div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Partner with us for CGM distribution</h1>
    <p>Expand access to advanced CGM solutions by joining our global distribution network. We work with qualified distributors to bring wearable biosensing technologies to healthcare markets worldwide.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WHY PARTNER WITH US ===== -->
<section class="bg-light" id="why-partner">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Why partner with us?</h2>
      <p>We provide the products, regulatory support, and market expertise you need to build a profitable CGM distribution business.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-4">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="21" x2="15" y2="9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Expand your portfolio</h4>
        <p>Offer your customers our factory-calibrated 14-day CGM system with clinically validated accuracy (MARD &lt;8%). Add advanced continuous glucose monitoring solutions to your existing healthcare or medical device product portfolio.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Faster market entry</h4>
        <p>Start selling sooner with our ready-to-go CGM system. We provide the hardware, mobile app, and cloud infrastructure and regulatory certificates, so you don't waste time on sensor tech and regulatory approval.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Brand customization</h4>
        <p>If you want to sell under your own brand, we support full customization including logo, packaging, labeling, and localized product identity. You can also choose to distribute under our existing brand, depending on your market strategy and positioning.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Higher margin potential</h4>
        <p>Our CGM delivers the same stability and accuracy as leading brands, yet at a more competitive cost. This gives you more room to compete in your local market and build stronger margins.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== BECOME A DISTRIBUTION PARTNER ===== -->
<section class="bg-white" id="become-partner">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="become-grid">
      <div class="become-text">
        <h2>Become a distribution partner</h2>
        <p>We're looking for qualified distributors who share our commitment to improving metabolic health through accessible CGM technology. Tell us about your market and distribution capabilities, and our team will reach out to explore a partnership.</p>
        <ul class="benefit-list">
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Exclusive territory rights for qualified partners</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Dedicated technical support</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Marketing materials and regulatory documentation provided</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#80bce2" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span>Competitive pricing with volume-based incentives</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-form">
        <h3>Get in touch</h3>
        <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="efeceb0a-a931-4c23-a3c6-e92b4bac78c5">
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Distributor inquiry from EverCheck website">
          <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="EverCheck Website">
          <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://evercheck.pages.dev/thank-you.html">
          <!-- Honeypot anti-spam -->
          <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="hidden" style="display:none;" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">E-mail</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="country">Country</label>
              <select id="country" name="country" required>
                <option value="">Select country</option>
                <option value="US">United States</option>
                <option value="GB">United Kingdom</option>
                <option value="DE">Germany</option>
                <option value="FR">France</option>
                <option value="JP">Japan</option>
                <option value="KR">South Korea</option>
                <option value="IN">India</option>
                <option value="BR">Brazil</option>
                <option value="AE">United Arab Emirates</option>
                <option value="SA">Saudi Arabia</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone">Phone</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="+1 234 567 890">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group form-full">
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us about your company, target market, and distribution experience..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-submit">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit inquiry</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FOOTER ===== -->

<!-- FOOTER CTA -->
<section class="section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-cta">
      <h2>Your long-term B2B CGM manufacturing partner</h2>
      <p>We combine self-developed CGM technologies with scalable manufacturing infrastructure to support healthcare brands worldwide.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact us now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
